        <h2>About the Internship</h2>
        <p>Cognifyz Technologies offers a Web Development Internship Program designed to provide hands-on experience in the field of web development. The program is structured to enhance coding skills and deepen understanding of industry best practices.The specific duration and details of each internship are outlined in the offer letter provided to selected candidates.Throughout the internship, participants work on real-world projects, receive mentorship from experienced developers, and have the opportunity to enhance their technical expertise in web development.For the most current information on available internship opportunities and their durations, it's advisable to visit Cognifyz Technologies' official website or contact their internship program coordinators directly.</p>
        <ul>Duration:
            <li><b>One-Month Internship:</b> Some programs are structured as intensive one-month internships, focusing on enhancing coding skills and providing practical experience in web development.</li>
            <li><b>Six-Month Internship:</b> Other opportunities extend to six months, allowing interns to gain deeper insights and develop their skills over a more extended period.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
