        <h2>Qualification</h2>
        <p>To apply for the Web Developer Internship at Cognifyz Technologies, candidates typically need to meet the following qualifications:</p>
        <h4><b>Educational Background:</b></h4>
        <ul>
            <li>Currently pursuing or recently completed a degree in Computer Science, Information Technology, or a related field.</li>
            <li>Candidates from non-technical backgrounds with strong web development skills may also be considered.</li>
        </ul>
        <h4><b>Technical Skills:</b></h4>
        <ul><b>Basic Knowledge:</b>
            <li>HTML, CSS, and JavaScript are mandatory.</li>
            <li>Understanding of responsive design and browser compatibility.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul><b>Advanced Skills (Preferred):</b>
            <li>Experience with frameworks like React, Angular, or Vue.js.</li>
            <li>Knowledge of backend technologies such as Node.js, PHP, or Python.</li>
            <li>Familiarity with databases like MySQL, MongoDB, or PostgreSQL.</li>
        </ul>
        <h4>Additional Requirements:</h4>
        <ul><b>Problem-Solving Skills:</b>
            <li>Ability to debug and optimize code efficiently.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul><b>Teamwork:</b>
            <li>Strong communication and collaboration skills to work effectively in a team environment.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul><b>Portfolio or Projects:</b>
            <li>Having a portfolio or GitHub repository showcasing previous projects is a plus.
            </li>
        </ul>
        <ul><b>Passion for Learning:</b>
            <li>Eagerness to explore new technologies and tools in web development.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul><b>Availability:</b>
            <li>Commitment to the internship duration (ranging from 1 to 6 months).</li>
